token_info.name: GENÓMICA 1
token_info.description: This interactive NFT is the world’s first virtual ecosystem of micro species created using machine learning and AI  — a concept of ‘Living Art’.  Click on the species to see them move. Press the logo for more info and Audio On/Off. Full screen option bottom right.  Collect 3 editions of this NFT and receive an additional collectable limited edition NFT featuring the 3 species of GENÓMICA 1. (Not applicable for secondary market).
